cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically in the area of reference modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of neural networks and deep learning, which suggests that it could also fit into cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with multimodal representations, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper mentions the use of Memory Networks, which suggests it could also fit into cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
